<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>주식 정보</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>주식 정보</h1>
    
    <form method="GET" action="/stocks">
        <label>주식 이름 검색: <input type="text" name="search" value="<%= search %>"></label>
        <button type="submit">검색</button>
    </form>

    <ul>
        <% stocks.forEach(stock => { %>
            <li>
                <form action="/trade" method="GET">
                    <button type="submit"><%= stock.stock_name %></button>
                </form>
                - 현재 가격: <%= stock.current_price %> 원 
                - 등락률: <%= stock.change_rate %>% 
                - 거래량: <%= stock.volume %> 주 
                - 순위: <%= stock.rank %>위
                - <a href="/stock/<%= stock.stock_id %>/orderbook">호가창 보기</a>
                - <a href="/stock/<%= stock.stock_id %>/transactions">주식 거래내역 보기</a>
            </li>
        <% }); %>
    </ul>

    <button onclick="location.href='/'">메인 페이지로 돌아가기</button>
</body>
</html>
